ing: 1 (11 ounce) can mandarin orange segments, drained
des: "This is a great hot salad to serve on a cold night.  This tastes great with any dish and can be changed according to your tastes."
ins: Pour the applesauce, cherry pie filling, sliced peaches, mandarin oranges, pineapple, brown sugar and cinnamon into a slow cooker. Cover, and cook on Low setting for 90 minutes.
